Korean Student Association, Tekstyles, Gamer's Guild, India Club, China Club, Asian American Student Union, Black Student Organization, NPHC, Office of International Education, OMED, Health Promotions, and more. You can grab some delicious grub, blow up stereotypes with water balloons, learn to Salsa and Reggae, and play some Japanese video games. (drops mic)
